<collectingCountry id="F33E766E553D56338E1C09A111A0F8A3" box="[103,216,1771,1804]" name="Somalia" pageId="6" pageNumber="279">Somalia</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B9636FE553D56338E1D085B134AF8F5" blockId="6.[100,1309,1338,3453]" pageId="6" pageNumber="279">
The species is also present in 
<collectingCountry id="F33E766E553D56338C67085B13B8F89D" box="[540,704,1809,1842]" name="Madagascar" pageId="6" pageNumber="279">Madagascar</collectingCountry>
and the Comoro Is, but their taxonomic situation thereis still unresolved.
